<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空很生气，说：“牛魔王骗了我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空飞快地回到洞门前，砸了洞门。哗啦！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛魔王跑了出来，大喊：“你这只坏猴子！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>竟然砸坏了我的门！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马上把那个扇子给我！”悟空大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不然，我就毁了你的整座山！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“绝对不可能！”牛魔王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空朝牛魔王冲过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！牛魔王变成鹤飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是只有他能变成别的动物。”悟空想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空变成了火凤凰，迅速去追鹤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他伸出爪子，朝鹤扑了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鹤朝更低的地方飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空没能抓住它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空往后看，可是鹤已经不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他跑哪儿去了？”悟空想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他往下看，看到一只羚羊正在田野上吃草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在那儿！”悟空落到地上变成了老虎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他悄悄地走进高高的草丛里，慢慢靠近羚羊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他扑了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道光闪过，羚羊变成了大白牛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大白牛朝天上飞去，悟空追了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他快要追上大白牛时，听到有人喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“退下，悟空！”原来是天兵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玉帝派我们来帮你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>更多的天兵朝大白牛冲过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大白牛哼了一声，转身朝另一个方向飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，另一些天兵们出现了，挡住了大白牛的去路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看着天兵们包围了大白牛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们靠近大白牛，用剑和枪对着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛魔王变回原形。“求你们不要伤害我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主急忙朝天兵们飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要伤害我丈夫！”她喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不是想要做坏事的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个天兵放下了剑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你真心悔过，我们就不会伤你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，现在你在妨碍唐僧西天取经。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孙悟空需要你的扇子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主把扇子递给了天兵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“扇子在这里。”她说，“我们知道错了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从现在起，我们会向善。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>求你们不要伤害我们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个天兵看了看牛魔王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛魔王点了点头。“我们保证。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好。”天兵说，“你们俩可以回到洞里去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，从现在起，不许惹祸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛魔王和他的夫人弯腰行礼后走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天兵把扇子递给了悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226890</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能有你来灭火焰山的火，真是太好了，悟空。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空有些疑惑。“为什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为是你放的那火。”天兵说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那时候，太上老君把你放进炼丹炉里，想要烧死你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你从里面逃了出来，把火弄得到处都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天，余火掉到这里，形成了火焰山。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看了看扇子。“我很高兴能灭火。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空回到村子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人又来到那个老人的家里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们再次向老人表示感谢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，沿着路走上了山坡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在山坡顶上，他们看着火焰山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空用力扇了一下扇子。呼！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火马上就灭了。空气凉爽了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看见山谷变绿了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>树上长出了叶子，到处开满了小花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鸟儿们在树上唱歌，动物们在草丛里跑来跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。很久以前，他做了很多坏事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他把一切都恢复了原状。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>